items.badge_description: Enjoying a nice Night Out on the town? Thanks for taking untappd along.
Total Beer Domination. We’re not worthy. That's over 200 different brews!

user.bio: I've come down from the violet skies to save the day.

items.badge_description: Round and round the wheel goes! Which style you’ll be drinking, nobody knows! Your desire to explore different styles is inspiring. Keep it up! That's a check-in to at least 35 different styles. Try 5 more for Level 8!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 20 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 5!

items.checkin_comment: I rarely ever give a beer a 5; let alone a lager. But this beer is incredible. I could (and did) drink this beer all day with ease. Perfect.

items.badge_description: Grab your stein and dawn your lederhosen because it’s time to trek through the mountains of one of the world's most historic beer regions. That's 10 different beers from a brewery located in Austria. Try 5 more for Level 3!

Wine isn't the only beverage worthy of pairing with a delicious meal. With so many styles widely available, there’s a perfect pint for any cuisine of your choosing. That's a beer at 5 different venues categories as a Restaurant. Try 5 more for Level 2!

Everyone loves fresh beer, but obviously not as much as you do. You went straight to the source. 

That's a beer at 5 different venues categorized as a Brewery. Visit 5 more different ones for Level 2!
